0.6
- Compatibility to Android 2.1
- Better Tablet experience: active listitem is marked.
- New FlightItem OLC gives Type, km and points.
- New FlightItem Landingtime.
- Flight tags are shown in FlightDetails.
- Reorganized Flightlistpreferences. One can nor select the order of elements,
	and one can sort by different criteria.
- BugFix: Missing decimal separator at OLC Speed.
